headline.main: Martin Scores 29, West Virginia Upends No. 12 Texas Women
headline.print_headline: Martin Scores 29, West Virginia Upends No. 12 Texas Women

lead_paragraph: Tynice Martin scored 29 points, Chiana Ray sank two clutch free throws and sixth-seeded West Virginia held on to topple twelfth-ranked and second-seeded Texas 62-59 in the semifinals of the Big 12 Conference Tournament on Sunday.
